      <abstract>
        <p>Correction of Aug 3 Man in the News article about George W Bush; Bush is not direct descendant of Pres Franklin Pierce</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>The front-page Man in the News article yesterday about George W. Bush misstated his family relationship to President Franklin Pierce. The relationship is through Mr. Bush's great-grandfather Scott Pierce, but Mr. Bush is not a direct descendant. None of Pierce's children survived to adulthood.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
